    <!-- Add Activity -->
     <activity>
        <statement>
            <p>
                <term>Work in Groups</term>
            </p>
            <p>
                A youth group in Kisumu County want to invest Ksh <m>10,000</m> for <m>3</m> years. The bank offers two investment options.
            </p>
            <p>
                Option A : The interest is calculated on the original amount for the period of investment.
            </p>
            <p>
                Option B : The interest is calculated on the original amount and the interest accumulated at the end of each year for the period of investment.
            </p>
            <p>
                If the interest rate is given to be <m>10 \%</m> p.a for both options.
            </p>
            <p>
                <term>In Groups</term> you are required to:
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(a)">
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Calculate using option A,
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ol marker="(i)">
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Interest earned each year for the three years?
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Total interest earned each year for the three years?
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Total amount at the end of three years?
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Does the interest earned change each year? What stays constant in the system? Why?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            Calculate using option B,
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ol marker="(i)">
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Interest earned each year for the three years?
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Total interest earned each year for the three years?
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <p>
                                        Total amount at the end of three years?
                                    </p>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Does the interest earned change each year? What is changing in the system? Why?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            <p>
                <term>Explore in your groups</term> how to express the interest and totals earned each year in option B in power form.
            </p>
            <p>
                Predict the amount after:
            </p>
            <p>
                <ol marker="(a)">
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            <m>4</m> years?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            <m>5</m> years?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <p>
                            <m>T</m> years?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ol>
            </p>
            
        </statement>
     </activity>

